(135, 12, 'usp_grid', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":\"uspcompov_custom\",\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"show_action\":\"false\",\"action_url\":null,\"grid_columns\":\"4\",\"spacing\":\"g-3\",\"items\":[{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/images\\/icon\\/usp_corp_overview\\/icon-customers.webp\",\"title\":\"OBSESSION FOR<br>CUSTOMERS\",\"title_id\":\"OBSESI TERHADAP<br>PELANGGAN\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n                                                        <li>&NoBreak;I start with my customers in mind in every decision I make.<\\/li>\\n                                                        <li>I go the extra mile to deliver beyond customers\' expectations.<\\/li>\\n                                                    <\\/ul>\",\"description_id\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n<li>&NoBreak;Saya selalu memprioritaskan pelanggan dalam setiap keputusan yang saya buat.<\\/li>\\n<li>Saya melakukan upaya ekstra untuk memberikan layanan yang melebihi harapan pelanggan.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/images\\/icon\\/usp_corp_overview\\/icon-change.webp\",\"title\":\"COURAGE FOR<br>CHANGE\",\"title_id\":\"KEBERANIAN UNTUK<br>PERUBAHAN\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n                                                        <li>&NoBreak;I fearlessly push boundaries and try new things.<\\/li>\\n                                                        <li>&NoBreak;I continuously adapt and improve to get better every day.<\\/li>\\n                                                    <\\/ul>\",\"description_id\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n\\n<li>&NoBreak;Saya dengan berani melampaui batasan dan mencoba hal-hal baru.<\\/li>\\n\\n<li>Saya terus beradaptasi dan meningkatkan diri untuk menjadi lebih baik setiap hari.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/images\\/icon\\/usp_corp_overview\\/icon-collaboration.webp\",\"title\":\"PASSION FOR COLLABORATION\",\"title_id\":\"SEMANGAT UNTUK BERKOLABORASI\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n                                                        <li>I build trust in all relationships to work towards common goals.<\\/li>\\n                                                        <li>I embrace diversity and learn from each other.<\\/li>\\n                                                    <\\/ul>\",\"description_id\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n\\n<li>Saya membangun kepercayaan dalam semua hubungan untuk bekerja menuju tujuan bersama.<\\/li>\\n\\n<li>Saya merangkul keberagaman dan belajar dari satu sama lain.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/images\\/icon\\/usp_corp_overview\\/icon-uncompromising-integrity.webp\",\"title\":\"UNCOMPROMISING INTEGRITY\",\"title_id\":\"INTEGRITAS TANPA KOMPROMI\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n                                                        <li>&NoBreak;I am honest, fair, and show ethical behaviour.<\\/li>\\n                                                        <li>&NoBreak;I am consistent and accountable for my actions.<\\/li>\\n                                                    <\\/ul>\",\"description_id\":\"<ul class=\\\"CheckList\\\">\\n\\n<li>Saya jujur, adil, dan menunjukkan perilaku etis.<\\/li>\\n\\n<li>Saya konsisten dan bertanggung jawab atas tindakan saya.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\",\"text_position\":\"left\"}],\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 02:44:31', '2026-02-24 05:27:17'),
(136, 12, 'information_list', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"false\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"MEDIA & ACTIVITIES\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Keep up with what\'s happening at Linknet\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Stay Update\"},\"info_sections\":[{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"Our Vision\",\"title_id\":\"Visi Kami\",\"content\":\"<p><strong>By 2027, To Be The First Choice in Every Business We Do<\\/strong><br><i>*Through the 4C\'s (Coverage. Capability, Cost, Capacity)<\\/i><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p><strong>Pada tahun 2027, Menjadi Pilihan Pertama dalam Setiap Bisnis yang Kami Lakukan<\\/strong><br><i>*Through the 4C\'s (Coverage. Capability, Cost, Capacity)<\\/i><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"About Linknet\",\"title_id\":\"Tentang Linknet\",\"content\":\"<p>The company was founded under the name PT Seruling Indah Permai in 1996 and then changed its name to PT Link Net TBK in 2000 with business activities in the field of trading goods and services. In 2011 and 2019 there were additional business activities, including activities in the field of providing cable telecommunications activities, multimedia services, internet, trade, and business management consulting services.On June 22 2022, the Company became part of the Axiata Group following the completion of the transaction to take over the Company\'s shares.<br><br>The Company operates Hybrid Fiber Coaxial (\\u201cHFC\\u201d) and Fiber To The Home (\\u201cFTTH\\u201d) cable systems with high technology and is capable of operating 870 MHz two-way broadband services.Currently PT Link Net Tbk is one of the largest private infrastructure and telecommunications network providers which has succeeded in building more than 4,000,000 Homepasses in more than 47 cities in Indonesia. We placed three Headends in strategic locations in the central business areas of Jakarta, Surabaya and Bali.<br><br>To maintain network frequency stability, we have placed several connecting hubs with redundant fiber optic circles connected to the Headend The company stretches across the Jabodetabek area, Bandung and its surroundings, Surabaya and its surroundings (including Malang, Gresik, Sidoarjo), Bali, Serang-Cilegon, Semarang, Solo, Medan, Batam, Cikampek-Purwakarta, Cirebon, Tegal, Yogyakarta and Kediri.<br><br>In mid-2014, the Company undertook steps to list PT Link Net Tbk as a public company or Tbk, and we carried out the Initial Public Offering (IPO) of its shares and listed on the Indonesian Stock Exchange on June 2, 2014 with Company\\u2019s stock code&nbsp;\\u201cLINK\\u201d.<br><br>Currently, Linknet is dedicated to improving lives and supporting Indonesia\\u2019s digital growth by delivering smart, reliable technology infrastructure through its three main business units. The new business units are FiberCo for fiber optic networks, EnterpriseCo for connectivity and B2B solutions, and MediaCo for content and media services. Link Net helps power the country\\u2019s digital future. With the purpose \\\"We LINK the Nation for Better Lives,\\\" the company stays focused on customers, encourages innovation and collaboration, and is committed to constantly getting better, aiming to deliver great results in everything it does.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perusahaan didirikan dengan nama PT Seruling Indah Permai pada tahun 1996 dan kemudian mengubah namanya menjadi PT Link Net Tbk pada tahun 2000 dengan kegiatan usaha di bidang perdagangan barang dan jasa. Pada tahun 2011 dan 2019, terdapat penambahan kegiatan usaha, termasuk kegiatan di bidang penyediaan layanan telekomunikasi kabel, layanan multimedia, internet, perdagangan, serta jasa konsultansi manajemen bisnis. Pada 22 Juni 2022, Perusahaan resmi menjadi bagian dari Axiata Group seiring dengan selesainya transaksi pengambilalihan saham Perusahaan.<\\/p><p>Perusahaan mengoperasikan sistem kabel Hybrid Fiber Coaxial (HFC) dan Fiber To The Home (FTTH) dengan teknologi tinggi yang mampu menjalankan layanan broadband dua arah pada frekuensi 870 MHz. Saat ini, PT Link Net Tbk merupakan salah satu penyedia infrastruktur dan jaringan telekomunikasi swasta terbesar yang telah berhasil membangun lebih dari 4.000.000 Homepasses di lebih dari 47 kota di Indonesia. Kami menempatkan tiga Headend di lokasi strategis di kawasan pusat bisnis Jakarta, Surabaya, dan Bali.<\\/p><p>Untuk menjaga stabilitas frekuensi jaringan, kami menempatkan beberapa hub penghubung dengan lingkaran serat optik redundan yang terhubung ke Headend. Jangkauan perusahaan membentang di wilayah Jabodetabek, Bandung dan sekitarnya, Surabaya dan sekitarnya (termasuk Malang, Gresik, Sidoarjo), Bali, Serang\\u2013Cilegon, Semarang, Solo, Medan, Batam, Cikampek\\u2013Purwakarta, Cirebon, Tegal, Yogyakarta, dan Kediri.<\\/p><p>Pada pertengahan 2014, Perusahaan melakukan langkah untuk mencatatkan PT Link Net Tbk sebagai perusahaan publik atau Tbk, dan kami melaksanakan Penawaran Umum Perdana (IPO) saham Perusahaan serta mencatatkannya di Bursa Efek Indonesia pada 2 Juni 2014 dengan kode saham \\u201cLINK\\u201d.<\\/p><p>Saat ini, Link Net berkomitmen untuk meningkatkan kualitas hidup dan mendukung pertumbuhan digital Indonesia dengan menyediakan infrastruktur teknologi yang cerdas dan andal melalui tiga unit bisnis utamanya. Unit bisnis baru tersebut meliputi FiberCo untuk jaringan serat optik, EnterpriseCo untuk konektivitas dan solusi B2B, serta MediaCo untuk layanan konten dan media. Link Net membantu menggerakkan masa depan digital Indonesia. Dengan tujuan \\u201cWe LINK the Nation for Better Lives\\u201d, Perusahaan tetap berfokus pada pelanggan, mendorong inovasi dan kolaborasi, serta berkomitmen untuk terus berkembang demi menghasilkan kinerja terbaik dalam setiap kegiatannya.<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"}]}', 3, 1, '2025-10-14 02:44:50', '2026-02-24 05:19:05'),
(138, 13, 'hero_section', '{\"title\": \"Milestone\", \"subtitle\": null, \"title_id\": null, \"custom_id\": \"lnSection__hero\", \"aria_label\": \"Our Vision\", \"button_icon\": \"arrow-top-right.svg\", \"button_link\": \"#\", \"button_size\": \"btn-lg\", \"button_text\": \"Get to Know Us\", \"description\": null, \"subtitle_id\": null, \"button_style\": \"btn-secondary-outline-reverse\", \"custom_class\": \"lnSection__hero\", \"pill_visible\": \"true\", \"button_text_id\": null, \"button_visible\": \"false\", \"description_id\": null, \"parallax_value\": 0.25, \"parallax_effect\": \"true\", \"background_image\": \"https://linknet.co.id/storage/files/1/urban-traffic-with-cityscape.jpg\", \"description_width\": \"w-75\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 03:15:28', '2025-10-14 03:16:09'),
(139, 13, 'information_list', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":\"MEDIA & ACTIVITIES\",\"intro_label_id\":null,\"intro_title\":\"Keep up with what\'s happening at Linknet\",\"intro_title_id\":null,\"intro_description\":\"Stay Update\",\"intro_description_id\":null,\"info_sections\":[{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"1996\",\"content\":\"<p>Establishment of the company under the name PT Seruling Indah Permai<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Pendirian perusahaan dengan nama PT Seruling Indah Permai<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"2000\",\"content\":\"<p>Name change to PT Link Net launch of Mynet Broadband Internet Service and Digital1<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perubahan nama menjadi PT Link Net serta peluncuran Layanan Internet Broadband Mynet dan Digital1<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"2007\",\"content\":\"<p>Launched High Speed Broadband Internet Service Fastnet<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Peluncuran Layanan Internet Broadband Berkecepatan Tinggi Fastnet<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"2008\",\"content\":\"<p>Acquired by PT First Media Tbk<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Diakuisisi oleh PT First Media Tbk<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"2010\",\"content\":\"<ol><li>Launched HD<\\/li><li>New Network Roll 0ut<\\/li><li>Launched Video On Demand Services<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"content_id\":\"<ol><li>Peluncuran layanan HD,<\\/li><li>pelaksanaan Roll Out Jaringan Baru,<\\/li><li>dan peluncuran Layanan Video On Demand.<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"}]}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 03:16:09', '2025-11-26 09:30:41'),
(140, 14, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/urban-traffic-with-cityscape.jpg\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"true\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Structure\",\"title_id\":\"Struktur Tata Kelola Perusahaan\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 03:18:43', '2025-11-26 08:11:45'),
(145, 15, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"true\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Corporate Governance Principal\",\"title_id\":\"Prinsip Tata Kelola Perusahaan\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 19:43:01', '2025-11-26 08:12:28'),
(147, 15, 'ckeditor', '{\"custom_id\":\"bodex\",\"custom_class\":\"bodex\",\"content\":\"<p>To protect the interests of all stakeholders and to increase its value to shareholders, the Company has been applying the principles of Good Corporate Governance in its line of business. In conducting its operations, the Company is committed to uphold business ethics and the principle of transparency, in accordance with prevailing laws and regulations.<\\/p><p>Good Corporate Governance has a significant impact towards the determination and the accomplishment of the Company\\u2019s goals, as well as in shaping and developing the Company\\u2019s corporate culture. For the Company, the implementation of Good Corporate Governance within its business process serves as a solid foundation in realizing the Company\\u2019s vision and mission. The Principles of Good Corporate Governance serves as a set of standards that aims to further enhance the Company\\u2019s image, efficiency, effectivity, and social responsibility. The Principles of Good Corporate Governance encompasses transparency, accountability, propriety, independence and responsibility.<\\/p><p>In implementing the principles of Good Corporate Governance, the Company has appointed a Corporate Secretary, established an Internal Audit Unit and Audit Committee, and appointed an Independent Commissioner and Independent Director. There is no other committee under the Board of Commissioners and Board of Directors of the Company, other than the Audit Committee.<\\/p>\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 19:51:49', '2025-11-26 10:04:53'),
(148, 16, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"true\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Corporate Governance Guidance\",\"title_id\":\"Panduan Tata Kelola Perusahaan\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 12:43:01', '2025-11-26 08:13:10'),
(149, 16, 'ckeditor', '{\"custom_id\":\"bodex\",\"custom_class\":\"bodex\",\"content\":\"<p>The implementation of good corporate governance is not only reflected by the visions, missions and values of The Company, but also by the Companies\\u2019 efforts to obey regulations in achieving the visions, missions and values. The Company, as part of the good corporate citizen, realizes that regulations are needed to regulate not only the Company\\u2019s external relations with the public but also the Company\\u2019s internal relations with its organs and employees. Therefore, the Company arranges a series of rules applied as corporate regulations.<\\/p><p>The Company\\u2019s corporate regulations are arranged in accordance with the philosophy of Pancasila and the National Development Program, where improvement in the economy and in the nation\\u2019s living standard is in need of supports from all the nations. Thus, the Company desires to role in Indonesia\\u2019s economic development not only by developing its business but also by developing and improve the competence of the human resources.<\\/p><p>The Company has determined that the management of human resources is part of its strategic development plan, in this way, the Company will be able to easily and persistently improve its ability to compete with other companies in Indonesia. The Company always believe that human resources are important assets for the Company\\u2019s sustainable growth and development for a long term. The Company\\u2019s existence is also important for its employee.<\\/p><p>The Company has considered various aspects so that it will be able to create a harmonious, save, steady, peaceful and dynamic relation between the Company and its entire employee. Among the aspects are certainty of duties, rights and obligations of all employees, attentions on employees\\u2019 needs during healthy and illness, and creation of working atmosphere supporting working environment. Those aspects are expected to be able to increase employee\\u2019s productivity and help in the creation of peacefulness and complacence for employees so that any problems that emerge can be solved amicably.<\\/p><p>The Corporate Regulations has been approved through a Decision Letter of Ministry of Manpower of the Republic of Indonesia, the Director General for Industrial Relations Development and Manpower Social Guarantee Number: KEP. 4\\/HI.00.00\\/00.0000.250707013\\/P-1\\/IX\\/2025 dated 3 September 2025 that will be valid until 2 September 2027. Generally, the Corporate Regulations contain the rights and obligations of employees and the company as well as rules aiming at the maintenance of harmonious, consistent and balance relations as part of attempts to increase efficiency, productivity and optimal achievements. The Corporate Regulations are expected to be able to realize the creation of conducive industrial relations between employees and the Company by paying attentions on the government\\u2019s regulations and laws, including their adjustment in the future.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Penerapan tata kelola perusahaan yang baik tidak hanya tercermin dari visi, misi dan nilai-nilai Perusahaan, tetapi juga oleh upaya Perusahaan untuk mematuhi peraturan dalam mencapai visi, misi dan nilai-nilai. Perseroan, sebagai bagian dari warga korporasi yang baik, menyadari bahwa regulasi diperlukan untuk mengatur tidak hanya hubungan eksternal Perseroan dengan publik tetapi juga hubungan internal Perseroan dengan organ dan karyawannya. Oleh karena itu, Perseroan menyusun serangkaian aturan yang berlaku sebagai peraturan perusahaan.<\\/p><p>Peraturan perusahaan Perseroan disusun sesuai dengan falsafah Pancasila dan Program Pembangunan Nasional, dimana peningkatan perekonomian dan taraf hidup bangsa sangat membutuhkan dukungan dari seluruh bangsa. Oleh karena itu, Perusahaan berkeinginan untuk berperan dalam pembangunan ekonomi Indonesia tidak hanya dengan mengembangkan bisnisnya tetapi juga dengan mengembangkan dan meningkatkan kompetensi sumber daya manusianya.<\\/p><p>Perseroan telah menetapkan bahwa pengelolaan sumber daya manusia merupakan bagian dari rencana strategis pengembangannya, dengan demikian Perseroan akan dapat dengan mudah dan gigih meningkatkan kemampuannya untuk bersaing dengan perusahaan lain di Indonesia. Perseroan selalu percaya bahwa sumber daya manusia merupakan aset penting bagi pertumbuhan dan perkembangan Perseroan yang berkelanjutan untuk jangka panjang. Eksistensi Perusahaan juga penting bagi karyawannya.<\\/p><p>Perseroan telah mempertimbangkan berbagai aspek sehingga mampu menciptakan hubungan yang harmonis, aman, tenteram, damai dan dinamis antara Perseroan dengan seluruh karyawannya. Diantaranya adalah kepastian tugas, hak dan kewajiban seluruh karyawan, perhatian terhadap kebutuhan karyawan selama sehat dan sakit, dan penciptaan suasana kerja yang mendukung lingkungan kerja. Aspek-aspek tersebut diharapkan mampu meningkatkan produktivitas pegawai dan membantu terciptanya ketentraman dan kepuasan kerja pegawai sehingga setiap permasalahan yang muncul dapat diselesaikan secara musyawarah.<\\/p><p>Peraturan Perusahaan telah disahkan melalui Surat Keputusan Kementerian Ketenagakerjaan Republik Indonesia, Direktur Jenderal Pembinaan Hubungan Industrial dan Jaminan Sosial Tenaga Kerja Nomor: KEP. 4\\/HI.00.00\\/00.0000.250707013\\/P-1\\/IX\\/2025 tanggal 3 September 2025 yang akan berlaku hingga 2 September 2027. Secara umum, Peraturan Perusahaan memuat hak dan kewajiban karyawan dan perusahaan serta ketentuan-ketentuan yang bertujuan menjaga hubungan yang harmonis, konsisten, dan seimbang sebagai bagian dari upaya meningkatkan efisiensi, produktivitas, dan pencapaian yang optimal. Peraturan Perusahaan diharapkan mampu mewujudkan terciptanya hubungan industrial yang kondusif antara karyawan dan Perusahaan dengan memperhatikan peraturan dan perundang-undangan pemerintah, termasuk penyesuaiannya di masa mendatang.<\\/p>\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 12:51:49', '2025-11-28 02:55:35'),
(150, 17, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"true\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Article Of Association\",\"title_id\":\"Anggaran Dasar\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 12:43:01', '2025-11-26 08:13:44'),
(151, 17, 'ckeditor', '{\"custom_id\":\"bodex\",\"custom_class\":\"bodex\",\"content\":\"<p>The Company established with name PT Seruling Indah Permai, based on Notarial Deed Number 93 dated March 14, 1996 of Dr. Misahardi Wilamarta, S.H., M.H., M.Kn, LL.M, Notary in Jakarta as amended by a Notarial Deed Number 304 dated July 26, 1996, which was drafted in front of Yuliandi Ermawanto, S.H., substitute notary of Misahardi Wilamarta, S.H., Notary in Jakarta. These Notarial Deeds have been approved by the Minister of Justice of the Republic of Indonesia based on a Decision Letter Number C2-8324 HT.01.01.Th.96 dated August 7, 1996 and has been published in the State Gazette of the Republic of Indonesia Number 96 dated November 29, 1996, Supplement Number 9456.<br><br>In 2020, the Company changed its name to PT Link Net based on Notarial Deed Number 35 dated March 28, 2000 of Myra Yuwono, S.H. Notary in South Jakarta which has been approved by the Minister of Law of the Republic of Indonesia based on a Decision Letter Number C-9118 HT.01.04.TH.2020. dated April 20, 2000 and has been published in the State Gazette of the Republic of Indonesia Number 84 dated October 20, 2000, Supplement Number 6296.<br><br>The latest amendments to the entire Articles of Association are contained in Notarial Deed Number 13 dated June 19, 2021 of Rini Yulianti, S.H. Notary South Jakarta, and Acceptance of Notification of Amendment to the Articles of Association by the Minister of Law and Human Rights of the Republic of Indonesia Number AHU-AH.01.03-0429788 dated June 19, 2021 which has been adjusted to the Regulation of the Financial Service Authority Number 15\\/POJK.04\\/2020 and other applicable laws and regulations in the capital market.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perseroan didirikan dengan nama PT Seruling Indah Permai, berdasarkan Akta Notaris No.93 tanggal 14 Maret 1996 dari Dr. Misahardi Wilamarta, SH, MH, M.Kn, LL.M, Notaris di Jakarta sebagaimana telah diubah dengan Akta Notaris Nomor 304 tanggal 26 Juli 1996 yang dibuat dihadapan Yuliandi Ermawanto, SH, Notaris Pengganti Misahardi Wilamarta, SH, Notaris di Jakarta. Akta Notaris ini telah mendapat pengesahan dari Menteri Kehakiman Republik Indonesia berdasarkan Surat Keputusan Nomor C2-8324 HT.01.01.Th.96 tanggal 7 Agustus 1996 dan telah diumumkan dalam Berita Negara Republik Indonesia. Nomor 96 tanggal 29 November 1996, Tambahan Nomor 9456.<\\/p><p>Pada tahun 2020, Perseroan berubah nama menjadi PT Link Net berdasarkan Akta Notaris Myra Yuwono, S.H. Nomor 35 tanggal 28 Maret 2000. Notaris di Jakarta Selatan yang telah disahkan oleh Menteri Hukum Republik Indonesia berdasarkan Surat Keputusan Nomor C-9118 HT.01.04.TH.2020. tanggal 20 April 2000 dan telah diumumkan dalam Lembaran Negara Republik Indonesia Nomor 84 tanggal 20 Oktober 2000, Tambahan Nomor 6296.<\\/p><p>Perubahan terakhir atas seluruh Anggaran Dasar tertuang dalam Akta Notaris Rini Yulianti, S.H. Nomor 13 tanggal 19 Juni 2021. Notaris Jakarta Selatan, dan Penerimaan Pemberitahuan Perubahan Anggaran Dasar oleh Menteri Hukum dan Hak Asasi Manusia Republik Indonesia Nomor AHU-AH.01.03-0429788 tanggal 19 Juni 2021 yang telah disesuaikan dengan Peraturan Menteri ini. Otoritas Jasa Keuangan Nomor 15\\/POJK.04\\/2020 dan peraturan perundang-undangan lainnya yang berlaku di bidang pasar modal.<\\/p>\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 12:51:49', '2025-11-27 07:35:54'),
(152, 18, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__hero\",\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"true\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Code of Conduct\",\"title_id\":\"Kode Etik\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-14 12:43:01', '2025-11-26 08:14:10');
INSERT INTO `page_components` (`id`, `page_id`, `component_type`, `component_data`, `sort_order`, `is_visible`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(153, 18, 'ckeditor', '{\"custom_id\":\"bodex\",\"custom_class\":\"bodex\",\"content\":\"<p>The Company\\u2019s commitment as a public company to obtain long term business sustainability is not only reflected on the Company\\u2019s compliance to binding regulations. The Company always implements a standard ethics and professional responsibilities as one of benchmarks in its efforts to achieve balance in business. Besides obligation to comply with the regulations and laws, the Company also implements the standard ethics and professional responsibilities as part of its responsibilities to the public, customers, shareholders and stakeholders in doing its business.<br><br>Under the guidance of the international standard, commitment to always obey the regulations, the implementation of good corporate governance, it is fundamentally important for the Company to determine the Code of Conduct and Professional Responsibility (Code of Conduct) that have been approved under a Resolution of the Board of Commissioners No. BOC-007\\/CSL-LN\\/VII\\/25 dated 7 August 2025. All management and employees are obliged to understand the Code of Conduct as the basis of implementation and behavior that regulate the relations between employees and the Company, among employees, customers, suppliers, shareholders, stakeholders, the government and the society. All management and employees are obliged to sign the standard code of Conduct every &nbsp;year.<br><br>Treatment on misappropriation towards the Corporate Regulations as well as the Code of Ethics and Professional Responsibilities is performed in a thorough investigation, which is based on facts, while the decision is made and issued based on the impacts of the actions, the level of consciousness and motives of the actions. Through a meticulous and objective consideration, the Board of Directors will decide on sanctions in accordance with the level of irregularities and the organizational hierarchy (the employees\\u2019 ranks or positions). Sanctions to employees include verbal reprimand, warning letters (I, II, III) as well as repudiation on wage increase, rank or bonuses, to the termination of employment. Specific on the termination of employment, an approval from the Directors need to be followed up by a request to the Manpower Department in line with regulations under the Law on Manpower of the Republic of Indonesia.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Komitmen Perseroan sebagai perusahaan publik untuk memperoleh keberlanjutan usaha jangka panjang tidak hanya tercermin dari kepatuhan Perseroan terhadap peraturan yang mengikat. Perseroan selalu menerapkan standar etika dan tanggung jawab profesional sebagai salah satu tolak ukur dalam upaya mencapai keseimbangan dalam bisnis. Selain kewajiban untuk mematuhi peraturan dan undang-undang, Perusahaan juga menerapkan standar etika dan tanggung jawab profesional sebagai bagian dari tanggung jawab kepada publik, pelanggan, pemegang saham dan pemangku kepentingan dalam menjalankan bisnisnya.<\\/p><p>Di bawah panduan standar internasional, komitmen untuk selalu mematuhi peraturan, serta penerapan tata kelola perusahaan yang baik, sangat penting bagi Perusahaan untuk menetapkan Kode Etik dan Tanggung Jawab Profesional (Code of Conduct) yang telah disetujui berdasarkan Keputusan Dewan Komisaris No. BOC-007\\/CSL-LN\\/VII\\/25 tanggal 7 Agustus 2025. Seluruh manajemen dan karyawan wajib memahami Kode Etik sebagai dasar pelaksanaan dan perilaku yang mengatur hubungan antara karyawan dan Perusahaan, antar karyawan, pelanggan, pemasok, pemegang saham, pemangku kepentingan, pemerintah, dan masyarakat. Seluruh manajemen dan karyawan wajib menandatangani Kode Etik standar setiap tahun.<\\/p><p>Perlakuan atas penyelewengan terhadap Peraturan Perusahaan serta Kode Etik dan Tanggung Jawab Profesi dilakukan dalam penyelidikan yang menyeluruh, yang didasarkan pada fakta, sedangkan keputusan dibuat dan dikeluarkan berdasarkan dampak dari tindakan, tingkat kesadaran dan motif tindakan. Melalui pertimbangan yang cermat dan objektif, Direksi akan memutuskan sanksi sesuai dengan tingkat penyimpangan dan hierarki organisasi (pangkat atau jabatan pegawai). Sanksi terhadap pegawai berupa teguran lisan, surat teguran (I, II, III) serta penolakan kenaikan upah, pangkat atau bonus, hingga pemutusan hubungan kerja. Khusus mengenai pemutusan hubungan kerja, persetujuan Direksi perlu ditindaklanjuti dengan permintaan kepada Departemen Tenaga Kerja sesuai dengan ketentuan Undang-Undang Ketenagakerjaan Republik Indonesia.<\\/p>\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-14 12:51:49', '2025-11-28 02:56:58'),
