INSERT INTO `page_components` (`id`, `page_id`, `component_type`, `component_data`, `sort_order`, `is_visible`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(199, 37, 'ckeditor', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"content\":\"<h3>INTRODUCTION<\\/h3><p>Link Net is committed to protecting the Privacy and data of our Data Subjects with utmost respect and due care. This Data Privacy Policy (referred to as \\u201cPolicy\\u201d) establishes the mandatory requirements of Axiata Group with respect to protection of Personal Data.<br>This is an overarching Policy and together with relevant underlying Privacy procedures, templates and guidelines provide the breadth and depth needed to meet Axiata Group\\u2019s Data Privacy requirements.<\\/p><h3>GUIDING PRINCIPLES<\\/h3><p>Link Net activities and Privacy practices are underpinned by the T.R.U.S.T. principles, which are laid out below:<\\/p><figure class=\\\"table\\\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Transparent<\\/th><td>We are TRANSPARENT about what, why and how we collect and protect YOUR PERSONAL DATA so that YOU can make informed decisions.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Rights<\\/th><td>We respect YOUR RIGHTS as individuals, so YOU are in control of YOUR PERSONAL DATA.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Use<\\/th><td>We USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA for specific and stated purposes and keep it for as long as required only.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Security<\\/th><td>We have established robust CYBER SECURITY PRACTICES in line with leading industry standards to protect YOUR PERSONAL DATA that YOU have shared with us.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Transfer<\\/th><td>With YOUR CONSENT or in accordance with APPLICABLE LAWS we may TRANSFER YOUR PERSONAL DATA and will take appropriate steps to ensure it is adequately protected.<\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><\\/figure><h3>SCOPE AND APPLICABILITY<\\/h3><p>This Policy applies to all Stakeholders of Axiata Group, which includes subsidiaries and associated companies that the Group has a controlling stake or ownership. Companies or entities in which Link Net does not have a controlling stake are encouraged to adopt this Policy.<br><br>This Policy shall apply to the end-to-end processing of Personal Data of customers, employees and all other stakeholders (collectively referred to as \\u201cData Subjects\\u201d), may it be in the form of digital, on paper or other materials. This Policy applies to all the employees, contract staff and vendors who process personal data on the Company\\u2019s behalf.<br><br>Link Net shall comply with Applicable Privacy Laws. To the extent this Policy contradicts or is inconsistent with requirements to any law, statute or regulation, the higher standards shall prevail.<\\/p><h3>DATA PRIVACY PRACTICES<\\/h3><p>In order to comply with and operationalize the T.R.U.S.T. principles, Link Net shall implement the following Data Privacy Practices:<\\/p><h4>LAWFULNESS, FAIRNESS, AND TRANSPARENCY<\\/h4><ol><li>Link Net shall process Personal Data lawfully, fairly and in a transparent manner. Link Net shall provide the data subjects with a Privacy Notice which specifies details on the purpose for which the Personal Data is being collected and processed, source of the Personal Data, class of the third parties to which the Personal Data is disclosed or may be disclosed to, security measures towards protection of Personal Data, data retention requirements, rights available to Data Subjects and other relevant information in line with Applicable Privacy Laws.<\\/li><li>Link Net shall process Personal Data when it is necessary and meets at least one of the following lawful bases for processing:<ol><li>where the Data Subject has given their consent for their Personal Data to be processed. Any processing shall be strictly within the purposes for which the consent is given;<\\/li><li>where the Processing is necessary for the performance of a contract with the Data Subject;<\\/li><li>where steps are to be taken at the request of the Data Subject with a view to entering into a contract;<\\/li><li>where the Processing is necessary to comply with legal obligations\\/regulatory requirement and for the exercise of any functions conferred on any person by or under any law;<\\/li><li>where it required for administration of justice and\\/or public interest for the purposes of state administration<\\/li><li>to protect the vital interests of Data Subjects<\\/li><li>any other lawful base for Processing Personal Data as stated by Applicable Privacy Laws.<\\/li><\\/ol><\\/li><li>Link Net shall also ensure that while Processing Sensitive Personal Data explicit consent is required of Data Subjects except for other lawful bases stated below:<ol><li>exercising or performing any right or obligation which is conferred or imposed by law on the Company in connection with employment<\\/li><li>any legal proceedings<\\/li><li>obtaining legal advice<\\/li><li>establishing, exercising or defending legal rights<\\/li><li>where the Processing is necessary to protect the vital interest of the Data Subject or another person<\\/li><li>any other lawful base for Processing Sensitive Personal Data as stated by Applicable Privacy Laws.<\\/li><\\/ol><\\/li><li>Link Net shall take reasonable steps to maintain accurate, complete, not misleading and up to date Personal Data only for the purpose(s) identified in the Privacy Notice.<\\/li><li>Link Net shall ensure that Personal Data collected and processed shall be adequate, relevant and not excessive for the purpose(s) identified in the Privacy Notice.<\\/li><\\/ol><h3>DATA SUBJECT RIGHTS<\\/h3><p>Link Net respects the rights of Data Subjects and shall provide them with the opportunity and platform to exercise their rights. Link Net shall establish processes for receiving, recording and responding to some or all of the below mentioned data subject rights in accordance with the Applicable Privacy Laws:<\\/p><ul><li>Right to be informed<\\/li><li>Right to access<\\/li><li>Right to correct personal data<\\/li><li>Right to withdraw consent<\\/li><li>Right to prevent Processing in certain circumstance (e.g. prevent direct marketing, Processing that is likely to cause distress)<\\/li><li>Right to erasure (to be forgotten)<\\/li><li>Right to data portability.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>RETENTION AND DISPOSAL<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall define and document retention periods for various categories of Personal Data in accordance with the stated purpose or as required by the law. Link Net shall ensure that Personal Data is retained as per the defined retention periods. Post expiry of the retention period, Personal Data shall be securely disposed or de-identified.<\\/p><h3>PRIVACY BY DESIGN<\\/h3><p>Privacy by Design is a methodology that enables Privacy to be built into the design and architecture of systems, products and processes.<br>Link Net shall adopt Privacy by Design methodology by ensuring Data Privacy issues are considered at the design phase of any system, service, product or process and then throughout the Personal Data lifecycle.<br>Link Net shall conduct Data Protection Impact Assessments (DPIAs) to identify underlying Privacy risks in the high-risk personal data Processing activities.<\\/p><h3>VENDOR PRIVACY MANAGEMENT AND CROSS-BORDER DATA TRANSFER<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall establish processes with respect to managing high- risk data processing vendors from a Data Privacy standpoint. The processes shall include the below tabulated activities:<\\/p><figure class=\\\"table\\\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Due Diligence<\\/th><td>Conduct out due diligence on the prospective high-risk vendor\\u2019s information security and Privacy posture prior to onboarding them<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Data Processing Agreements<\\/th><td>Include adequate Privacy and information security clauses in the contractual agreement executed with the vendors<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Periodic Vendor Assessment<\\/th><td>Carry out periodic assessment of the existing high-risk vendors\\u2019 compliance with contractual and regulatory obligations<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>DPIAs for Projects<\\/th><td>Carry out DPIAs prior to onboarding high-risk projects from existing vendors<\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><\\/figure><p>Link Net shall assess the permissibility of Cross-Border Data Transfers in accordance with Applicable Privacy Laws. Further, Link Net shall also ensure that necessary safeguards (such as Data Transfer Agreements) are in place to protect all the Cross-Border Data Transfers.<\\/p><h3>PRIVACY INCIDENT AND DATA BREACH MANAGEMENT<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall define and implement a process for reporting, assessing, resolving, communicating, escalating, notifying, and performing of any other actions required in the effective management of Privacy incidents and data breaches.<\\/p><h3>SECURITY<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall implement appropriate technical safeguards and organizational measures to maintain the confidentiality, integrity and availability of Personal Data.<\\/p><h3>AUDIT, REVIEW AND REPORTING<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall carry out periodic Privacy audits on their data Processing environment to monitor its compliance against this Policy, Group Privacy standards and Applicable Privacy Laws.<\\/p><h3>TRAINING AND AWARENESS<\\/h3><p>Link Net shall mandate annual Data Privacy awareness trainings for their employees and contract staff. Link Net shall also raise awareness through knowledge sharing sessions, e-mailers, posters, Privacy campaigns and other such means.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<h3>PENDAHULUAN<\\/h3><p>Link Net berkomitmen untuk melindungi Privasi dan Subyek Data kami dengan penuh hormat dan kehati-hatian. Kebijakan Privasi Data ini (disebut sebagai \\u201cKebijakan\\u201d) menetapkan persyaratan wajib Grup Axiata sehubungan dengan perlindungan Data Pribadi.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Ini adalah Kebijakan menyeluruh dan bersama dengan prosedur, templat, dan pedoman Privasi mendasar yang relevan memberikan keluasan dan kedalaman yang diperlukan untuk memenuhi persyaratan Privasi Data Grup Axiata.<\\/p><h3>PRINSIP PEDOMAN<\\/h3><p>Aktivitas Link Net dan praktek Privasi didukung oleh prinsip-prinsip T.R.U.S.T sebagaimana diuraikan di bawah ini:<\\/p><figure class=\\\"table\\\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Transparent<\\/th><td>Kami TRANSPARAN tentang apa, mengapa dan bagaimana kami mengumpulkan dan melindungi DATA PRIBADI ANDA sehingga ANDA dapat membuat keputusan yang tepat.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Rights<\\/th><td>Kami menghormati HAK ANDA sebagai individu, sehingga ANDA memegang kendali atas DATA PRIBADI ANDA.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Use<\\/th><td>Kami MENGGUNAKAN DATA PRIBADI ANDA untuk tujuan tertentu dan dinyatakan dan menyimpannya selama diperlukan saja.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Security<\\/th><td>Kami telah menetapkan PRAKTIK KEAMANAN CYBER yang kuat sejalan dengan standar industri terkemuka untuk melindungi DATA PRIBADI ANDA yang telah ANDA bagikan kepada kami.<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Transfer<\\/th><td>Dengan PERSETUJUAN ANDA atau sesuai dengan HUKUM YANG BERLAKU, kami dapat MENGALIHKAN DATA PRIBADI ANDA dan akan mengambil langkah-langkah yang tepat untuk memastikannya dilindungi secara memadai.<\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><\\/figure><h3>RUANG LINGKUP DAN PENERAPAN<\\/h3><p>Kebijakan ini berlaku untuk semua Pemangku Kepentingan Grup Axiata, termasuk anak perusahaan dan perusahaan asosiasi yang saham atau kepemilikannya menjadi pengendali Grup. Perusahaan atau entitas di mana Link Net tidak memiliki saham pengendali dianjurkan untuk mengadopsi kebijakan ini.<br><br>Kebijakan ini wajib berlaku untuk pemrosesan Data Pribadi pelanggan, karyawan, dan semua pemangku kepentingan lainnya secara end-to-end (secara bersama-sama disebut sebagai \\u201cSubyek Data\\u201d), baik dalam bentuk digital, di atas kertas, atau materi lainnya. Kebijakan ini berlaku untuk seluruh karyawan, karyawan kontrak dan vendor yang mengelola data pribadi atas nama Perusahaan.<br><br>Link Net wajib mematuhi Hukum Privasi yang Berlaku. Sejauh Kebijakan ini bertentangan atau tidak konsisten dengan persyaratan hukum, undang-undang atau peraturan apa pun, standar yang lebih tinggi wajib berlaku.<\\/p><h3>PRAKTEK PRIVASI DATA<\\/h3><p>Untuk mematuhi dan menjalankan prinsip T.R.U.S.T., Link Net wajib menerapkan Praktik Privasi Data berikut:<\\/p><p>HUKUM, KEADILAN dan TRANSPARANSI<\\/p><ol><li>Link Net wajib memproses Data Pribadi secara sah, adil, dan transparan. Link Net wajib memberikan Pemberitahuan Privasi kepada subyek data yang menjelaskan detail tujuan di mana Data Pribadi dikumpulkan dan diproses, sumber Data Pribadi, kelas pihak ketiga di mana Data Pribadi diungkapkan atau dapat diungkapkan kepada, tindakan keamanan terhadap perlindungan Data Pribadi, persyaratan penyimpanan data, hak yang tersedia untuk Subyek Data dan informasi relevan lainnya, sejalan dengan Hukum Privasi yang Berlaku.<\\/li><li>Link Net wajib memproses Data Pribadi bila diperlukan dan memenuhi setidaknya salah satu dasar hukum berikut untuk diproses:<ol><li>di mana Subyek Data telah memberikan persetujuan mereka untuk memproses Data Pribadi mereka. Pemrosesan apa pun<\\/li><li>di mana Pemrosesan diperlukan untuk pelaksanaan kontrak dengan Subyek Data;<\\/li><li>di mana langkah-langkah harus diambil atas permintaan Subyek Data dengan maksud untuk mengadakan kontrak;<\\/li><li>di mana Pemrosesan diperlukan untuk mematuhi kewajiban hukum\\/persyaratan peraturan dan untuk pelaksanaan fungsi<\\/li><li>dalam hal diperlukan untuk penyelenggaraan peradilan dan\\/atau kepentingan umum untuk kepentingan penyelenggaraan<\\/li><li>untuk melindungi kepentingan vital Subyek Data<\\/li><li>dasar sah lainnya untuk Memproses Data Pribadi sebagaimana dinyatakan oleh Hukum Privasi yang Berlaku.<\\/li><\\/ol><\\/li><li>Link Net juga wajib memastikan bahwa saat Memproses Data Pribadi Sensitif persetujuan eksplisit diperlukan dari Subyek Data kecuali untuk dasar sah lainnya yang dinyatakan di bawah ini:<ol><li>menjalankan atau melakukan setiap hak atau kewajiban yang diberikan atau dipaksakan oleh undang-undang kepada Perusahaan sehubungan dengan pekerjaan<\\/li><li>proses hukum apapun<\\/li><li>memperoleh nasihat hukum<\\/li><li>membangun, melaksanakan atau membela hak-hak hukum<\\/li><li>jika Pemrosesan diperlukan untuk melindungi kepentingan vital Subyek Data atau orang lain<\\/li><li>dasar sah lainnya untuk Memproses Data Pribadi Sensitif sebagaimana dinyatakan oleh Undang-Undang Privasi yang Berlaku.<\\/li><\\/ol><\\/li><li>Link Net wajib mengambil langkah-langkah yang wajar untuk memelihara akurasi, kelengkapan, tidak menyesatkan dan terkini Data Pribadi hanya untuk tujuan-tujuan yang disebutkan dalam Pemberitahuan Privasi.<\\/li><li>Link Net wajib memastikan bahwa Data Pribadi yang dikumpulkan dan diproses wajib memadai, relevan, dan tidak berlebihan untuk tujuan-tujuan yang disebutkan dalam Pemberitahuan Privasi.<\\/li><\\/ol><h3>HAK SUBYEK DATA<\\/h3><p>Link Net menghormati hak Subyek Data dan wajib memberi mereka kesempatan dan platform untuk menggunakan hak mereka. Perusahaan wajib menetapkan proses untuk menerima, merekam, dan menanggapi beberapa atau semua hak subyek data yang disebutkan di bawah sesuai dengan Undang-Undang Privasi yang Berlaku:<\\/p><ul><li>Hak untuk diberitahu;<\\/li><li>Hak untuk mengakses;<\\/li><li>Hak untuk memperbaiki data pribadi;<\\/li><li>Hak untuk menarik persetujuan;<\\/li><li>Hak untuk mencegah Pemrosesan dalam keadaan tertentu (misal: mencegah pemasaran langsung, Pemrosesan yang mungkin menyebabkan kesulitan);<\\/li><li>Hak menghapus (untuk dilupakan);<\\/li><li>Hak atas portabilitas data.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3>RETENSI dan PEMUSNAHAN<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib menentukan dan mendokumentasikan periode penyimpanan untuk berbagai kategori Data Pribadi sesuai dengan tujuan yang dinyatakan atau sebagaimana diwajibkan oleh undang-undang. Link Net wajib memastikan bahwa Data Pribadi disimpan sesuai dengan periode penyimpanan yang ditentukan. Setelah berakhirnya periode penyimpanan, Data Pribadi wajib dibuang atau dihilangkan identitasnya dengan aman.<\\/p><h3>PRIVASI BERDASARKAN DESAIN<\\/h3><p>Privacy by Design adalah metodologi yang memungkinkan Privasi dibangun ke dalam desain dan arsitektur dari sistem, produk dan proses.<\\/p><p>Link Net wajib mengadopsi metodologi Privasi dengan Desain dengan memastikan masalah Privasi Data dipertimbangkan pada tahap desain sistem, layanan, produk atau proses apa pun dan kemudian di seluruh siklus hidup Data Pribadi.<\\/p><p>Link Net wajib melakukan Penilaian Dampak Perlindungan Data (DPIA) untuk mengidentifikasi risiko Privasi yang mendasari aktivitas Pemrosesan data pribadi berisiko tinggi.<\\/p><h3>MANAJEMEN PRIVASI VENDOR DAN TRANSFER DATA LINTAS BATAS<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib menetapkan proses sehubungan dengan pengelolaan vendor pemrosesan data berisiko tinggi dari sudut pandang Privasi Data. Proses wajib mencakup kegiatan tabulasi di bawah ini:<\\/p><figure class=\\\"table\\\"><table><tbody><tr><th>Uji Tuntas<\\/th><td>Lakukan uji tuntas pada keamanan informasi dan postur Privasi calon vendor berisiko tinggi sebelum melakukan orientasi<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Perjanjian Pemrosesan Data<\\/th><td>Sertakan klausul Privasi dan keamanan informasi yang memadai dalam perjanjian kontrak yang ditandatangani dengan vendor<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>Penilaian Vendor Berkala<\\/th><td>Lakukan penilaian berkala terhadap kepatuhan vendor berisiko tinggi terhadap kewajiban kontrak dan peraturan<\\/td><\\/tr><tr><th>DPIAs untuk Proyek<\\/th><td>Melaksanakan DPIA sebelum melakukan onboarding proyek berisiko tinggi dari vendor yang ada<\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><\\/figure><p>Link Net wajib menilai izin Transfer Data Lintas Batas sesuai dengan Hukum Privasi yang Berlaku. Selanjutnya, Link Net juga wajib memastikan bahwa perlindungan yang diperlukan (seperti Perjanjian Transfer Data) tersedia untuk melindungi semua Transfer Data Lintas Batas.<\\/p><h3>INSIDEN PRIVASI DAN MANAJEMEN PELANGGARAN DATA<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib menetapkan dan menerapkan proses untuk melaporkan, menilai, menyelesaikan, mengkomunikasikan, meningkatkan, memberi tahu, dan melakukan tindakan lain yang diperlukan dalam manajemen yang efektif atas insiden Privasi dan pelanggaran data.<\\/p><h3>KEAMANAN<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib menerapkan pengamanan teknis dan tindakan organisasi yang sesuai untuk menjaga kerahasiaan, integritas, dan ketersediaan Data Pribadi<\\/p><h3>AUDIT, REVIEW DAN PELAPORAN<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib melakukan audit Privasi berkala pada lingkungan Pemrosesan data mereka untuk memantau kepatuhannya terhadap Kebijakan ini, standar Privasi Grup, dan Hukum Privasi yang Berlaku<\\/p><h3>PELATIHAN DAN KESADARAN<\\/h3><p>Link Net wajib mengamanatkan pelatihan kesadaran Privasi Data tahunan untuk karyawan dan staf kontrak mereka. Link Net juga wajib meningkatkan kesadaran melalui sesi berbagi pengetahuan, e-mail, poster, kampanye Privasi dan sarana lainnya.<\\/p>\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-21 10:59:42', '2025-11-27 08:12:29'),
(200, 38, 'tradingview_symbol_overview', '{\"custom_id\":\"\",\"custom_class\":\"\",\"symbol\":\"IDX:LINK\",\"interval\":\"1D\",\"widget_height\":500,\"theme\":\"light\",\"locale\":\"en\",\"chart_type\":\"area\",\"line_type\":\"0\",\"line_width\":2,\"hide_date_ranges\":false,\"hide_market_status\":false,\"hide_symbol_logo\":false}', 1, 1, '2025-10-26 20:41:28', '2025-10-26 20:41:31'),
(201, 39, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessbg.jpg\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/enterprise.svg\",\"pill_visible\":\"false\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Let\'s Transform Your Connectivity to be Versatile\",\"title_id\":\"Transformasikan konektivitas menjadi lebih fleksibel dan serbaguna\",\"description\":\"B2B Connectivity & Solutions\",\"description_id\":\"Konektivitas & Solusi B2B\",\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"true\",\"button_text\":\"Visit Enteprise Website\",\"button_text_id\":\"Kunjungi Website Enteprise\",\"button_link\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.id\\/\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-26 21:02:23', '2025-11-26 09:46:11'),
(202, 39, 'usp_grid', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":null,\"intro_label_id\":null,\"intro_title\":\"World Class Connectivity\",\"intro_title_id\":\"Konektivitas Kelas Dunia\",\"intro_description\":\"Linknet Enterprise is a trusted provider of integrated technology, data communication, and connectivity solutions that help businesses navigate the demands of digital transformation. Backed by a strong portfolio of over 3,300 loyal customers, we deliver secure, reliable, and high-performance internet and ICT services tailored to enterprise needs.\\n\\nAs we continue to strengthen our position in the enterprise segment, we are also expanding our support for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs), enabling organizations of all sizes to grow and stay competitive in a dynamic digital landscape.\",\"intro_description_id\":\"Linknet Enterprise adalah penyedia terpercaya untuk solusi teknologi terintegrasi, komunikasi data, dan konektivitas yang membantu bisnis menghadapi tuntutan transformasi digital. Didukung oleh portofolio kuat dengan lebih dari 3.300 pelanggan loyal, kami menyediakan layanan internet dan ICT yang aman, andal, serta berkinerja tinggi yang disesuaikan dengan kebutuhan perusahaan.\\n\\nSeiring kami terus memperkuat posisi di segmen enterprise, kami juga memperluas dukungan bagi usaha kecil dan menengah (UKM), memungkinkan organisasi dari berbagai skala untuk tumbuh dan tetap kompetitif di lanskap digital yang dinamis.\",\"show_action\":\"false\",\"action_text\":\"See Enterprise Product\",\"action_text_id\":\"See Enterprise Product\",\"action_url\":\"#\",\"grid_columns\":\"4\",\"spacing\":\"g-3\",\"items\":[{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon.svg\",\"title\":\"4M+ Homepasses\",\"title_id\":\"4M+ Homepasses\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Spread across more than 47 major cities in Indonesia\",\"description_id\":\"Menjangkau lebih dari 47 kota besar di seluruh Indonesia\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-1.svg\",\"title\":\"25 Years of Service\",\"title_id\":\"25 Tahun Layanan\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Since 1996, we have been present to build Indonesian connectivity.\",\"description_id\":\"Sejak 1996, kami hadir untuk membangun konektivitas Indonesia\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-2.svg\",\"title\":\"3 Pillars of Business\",\"title_id\":\"3 Pilar Bisnis\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"FiberCo, EnterpriseCo, and MediaCo for complete solutions\",\"description_id\":\"FiberCo, EnterpriseCo, dan MediaCo untuk solusi yang lengkap\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-3.svg\",\"title\":\"3 Strategic Headend\",\"title_id\":\"3 Strategic Headend\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Located in the business center of Jakarta, Surabaya, and Bali\",\"description_id\":\"Berlokasi di pusat bisnis Jakarta, Surabaya dan Bali\",\"text_position\":\"left\"}],\"bg_type\":\"image\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/map-indonesia-dots.svg\",\"bg_position\":\"center\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-26 21:06:29', '2025-11-26 09:52:11'),
(203, 39, 'list_services', '{\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"PRODUCT\",\"id\":\"PRODUK\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Discover Our Services at Linknet Enterprise\",\"id\":\"Temukan Layanan Kami di Linknet Enterprise\"},\"intro_desc\":{\"en\":null,\"id\":null},\"services\":[{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/values\\/values-customers.png\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"Connectivity\",\"id\":\"Konektivitas\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Provide smooth data transactions between branch offices securely, stably and efficiently through reliable connectivity services.\",\"id\":\"Berikan kelancaran transaksi data antar kantor cabang secara aman, stabil dan efisien melalui layanan konektivitas andal.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Dedicated Internet\",\"id\":\"Internet Dedicated\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Leased Line\",\"id\":\"Leased Line\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"IP Transit\",\"id\":\"IP Transit\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"VSAT HTS\",\"id\":\"VSAT HTS\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"MPLS\",\"id\":\"MPLS\"}}],\"other_count\":\"10+ Others\"},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"ICT Solutions\",\"id\":null},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Layanan terintegrasi cloud, keamanan data, dan manajemen IT untuk mendukung transformasi digital. Solusi fleksibel dengan teknologi terkini untuk efisiensi dan daya saing bisnis masa depan.\",\"id\":null},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Penetration Test\",\"id\":\"Penetration Test\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Firewall\",\"id\":\"Firewall\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Anti DDOS\",\"id\":\"Anti DDOS\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"SD WAN\",\"id\":\"SD WAN\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Cloud\",\"id\":\"Cloud\"}}],\"other_count\":\"6+ Others\"},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"Professional Service\",\"id\":null},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Layanan dukungan teknis menyeluruh untuk memastikan infrastruktur IT andal, efisien, dan mendukung produktivitas serta pertumbuhan bisnis Anda.\",\"id\":null},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Managed Service\",\"id\":\"Managed Service\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Engineer on Site\",\"id\":\"Engineer on Site\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"IT Network\",\"id\":\"IT Network\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Corporate TV\",\"id\":\"Corporate TV\"}},{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Voice\",\"id\":\"Voice\"}}],\"other_count\":\"1+ Others\"}]}', 3, 1, '2025-10-26 21:21:32', '2025-10-26 21:59:36'),
(205, 39, 'info_contacts', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__infoContact\",\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":null,\"intro_label_id\":null,\"intro_title\":\"Get More Information about Linknet EnterpriseCo\",\"intro_title_id\":null,\"intro_description\":\"Have questions or need more information? Our team is here to help. Reach out to us and we\'ll respond as soon as possible.\",\"intro_description_id\":null,\"show_contacts_section\":\"true\",\"contact_items\":[{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/world.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Website\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"www.linknet.id\"},\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.id\",\"target\":\"_blank\"},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/phone.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Phone\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"(021) 29536838\"},\"url\":\"tel:+622129536838\",\"target\":null},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/mail.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Email\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"enterprise.inquiry@linknet.co.id\"},\"url\":\"mailto:enterprise.inquiry@linknet.co.id\",\"target\":null}]}', 4, 1, '2025-10-26 21:55:12', '2025-11-26 04:28:00'),
(206, 40, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/assets\\/bg\\/ln-fiber-desktop.jpg\",\"background_image_mobile\":null,\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__medium\",\"theme\":\"light\",\"gradient_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_image\":\"\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/assets\\/logo\\/logo-LNF-white.png\",\"pill_visible\":\"false\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"Discover the Next Level of Internet Speed with Fiber Optics\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Fiber Optic Networks\"},\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"true\",\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Visit FiberCo Website\"},\"button_link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linknetfiber.id\\/\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-26 14:02:23', '2025-11-30 16:55:27'),
(207, 40, 'usp_grid', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"We provide the best fiber connectivity for you\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"At Linknet Fiber, we are dedicated to delivering the ultimate internet experience with our cutting-edge fiber optic technology. As the leading provider in the industry, we offer unparalleled speed, reliability, and performance, ensuring seamless connectivity for all your online needs. Whether you\'re streaming high-definition videos, engaging in immersive online gaming, or managing a smart home, our fiber optic solutions provide the robust bandwidth and low latency required for a flawless digital experience.\\n\\nJoin the thousands of satisfied customers who have made the switch to Linknet Fiber. Our commitment to innovation and customer satisfaction sets us apart, making us the preferred choice for those who demand the best. Upgrade to Linknet Fiber today and experience the difference of truly high-speed internet.\"},\"show_action\":\"false\",\"action_text\":{\"en\":\"See Enterprise Product\"},\"action_url\":\"#\",\"grid_columns\":\"4\",\"spacing\":\"g-3\",\"items\":[{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon.svg\",\"title\":\"Large, increasing coverage with proven partners\",\"title_id\":\"Large, increasing coverage with proven partners\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Large existing base of 4 Millions homepassed in attractive areas.\",\"description_id\":\"Large existing base of 4 Millions homepassed in attractive areas.\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-1.svg\",\"title\":\"Better experienced than other FiberCos\",\"title_id\":\"Better experienced than other FiberCos\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Focused on network rollout and management after the ongoing carve-out of retail business.\",\"description_id\":\"Focused on network rollout and management after the ongoing carve-out of retail business.\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-2.svg\",\"title\":\"Superior services\",\"title_id\":\"Superior services\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Have retail business experience, therefore can give much better service as compared to pure FiberCos.\",\"description_id\":\"Have retail business experience, therefore can give much better service as compared to pure FiberCos.\",\"text_position\":\"left\"}],\"bg_type\":\"image\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/map-indonesia-dots.svg\",\"bg_position\":\"center\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-26 14:06:29', '2025-11-30 17:06:17'),
(208, 40, 'list_services', '{\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"PRODUCT\",\"id\":\"PRODUK\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Discover Our Services at Linknet Fiber\",\"id\":\"Temukan Layanan Kami di Linknet Fiber\"},\"services\":[{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/values\\/values-customers.png\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"Build to Suit FTTH Network\",\"id\":\"Konektivitas\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"With our Build to Suit FTTH services, we develop fiber optic network infrastructure based on each client\'s specific location and needs,\\u00a0 ensuring fast and stable internet connectivity.\",\"id\":\"Berikan kelancaran transaksi data antar kantor cabang secara aman, stabil dan efisien melalui layanan konektivitas andal.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"FTTH services\",\"id\":\"FTTH services\"}}],\"other_count\":null},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"Data Center Services\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Our Data Center Services offer secure storage for digital data, critical information, and business applications, with strong protection against cyber threats and natural disasters, ensuring your business remains adaptive and resilient.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"other_count\":null},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"NAP Services (IP Transit)\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Our NAP services (IP Transit) enable ISPs to send and receive data through reliable, high-capacity routes, ensuring that data travels in a more direct, faster, and stable manner without passing through multiple intermediary networks.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"other_count\":null}]}', 3, 1, '2025-10-26 14:21:32', '2026-01-14 07:37:09'),
(209, 40, 'info_contacts', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__infoContact\",\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"true\",\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Get More Information about Linknet Fiber\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Have questions or need more information? Our team is here to help. Reach out to us and we\'ll respond as soon as possible.\"},\"show_contacts_section\":\"true\",\"contact_items\":[{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/world.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Website\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"linknetfiber.id\"},\"url\":\"linknetfiber.id\",\"target\":\"_blank\"},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/phone.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Phone\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"0877-8277-5525\"},\"url\":\"tel:+087782775525\",\"target\":null},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/mail.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Email\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"info.fiberco@linknet.co.id\"},\"url\":\"mailto:info.fiberco@linknet.co.id\",\"target\":null}]}', 4, 1, '2025-10-26 14:55:12', '2026-01-14 07:39:27'),
(210, 41, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/assets\\/bg\\/ln-media-desktop.jpg\",\"background_image_mobile\":null,\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__medium\",\"theme\":\"light\",\"gradient_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/mediaco.svg\",\"pill_visible\":\"false\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"Your Gateway to Quality Content and Smarter Media\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Content & Media Services\"},\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"true\",\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Visit MediaCo Website\"},\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-10-26 14:02:23', '2025-11-30 07:48:06'),
(211, 41, 'usp_grid', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":null,\"intro_label_id\":null,\"intro_title\":\"Entertain The Nation\",\"intro_title_id\":\"Entertain The Nation\",\"intro_description\":\"Linknet Media\\u00a0is a growing Pay TV platform offering premium content from trusted partners for both residential and business customers. We provide flexible linear and ondemand (VOD) viewing experiences, complemented by integrated Media Sales solutions to support effective content distribution and monetization. Backed by advanced technology and a broad network of partners, we are ready to become your strategic partner for all your entertainment and media needs.\",\"intro_description_id\":\"Linknet Media adalah platform Pay TV yang terus berkembang, menawarkan konten premium dari mitra terpercaya untuk pelanggan residensial maupun bisnis. Kami menyediakan pengalaman menonton yang fleksibel, baik linear maupun on-demand (VOD), yang dilengkapi dengan solusi Media Sales terintegrasi untuk mendukung distribusi konten dan monetisasi yang efektif. Didukung oleh teknologi canggih dan jaringan kemitraan yang luas, kami siap menjadi mitra strategis Anda untuk seluruh kebutuhan hiburan dan media.\",\"show_action\":\"false\",\"action_text\":\"See MediaCo Product\",\"action_text_id\":\"See MediaCo Product\",\"action_url\":\"#\",\"grid_columns\":\"4\",\"spacing\":\"g-3\",\"items\":[{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon.svg\",\"title\":\"4M+ Homepasses\",\"title_id\":\"4M+ Homepasses\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Spread across more than 47 major cities in Indonesia\",\"description_id\":\"Menjangkau lebih dari 47 kota besar di seluruh Indonesia\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-1.svg\",\"title\":\"25 Years of Service\",\"title_id\":\"25 Tahun Layanan\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Since 1996, we have been present to build Indonesian connectivity.\",\"description_id\":\"Sejak 1996, kami hadir untuk membangun konektivitas Indonesia\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-2.svg\",\"title\":\"3 Pillars of Business\",\"title_id\":\"3 Pilar Bisnis\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"FiberCo, EnterpriseCo, and MediaCo for complete solutions\",\"description_id\":\"FiberCo, EnterpriseCo, dan MediaCo untuk solusi yang lengkap\",\"text_position\":\"left\"},{\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/businessenterprise\\/icon-3.svg\",\"title\":\"3 Strategic Headend\",\"title_id\":\"3 Strategic Headend\",\"label\":null,\"label_id\":null,\"description\":\"Located in the business center of Jakarta, Surabaya, and Bali\",\"description_id\":\"Berlokasi di pusat bisnis Jakarta, Surabaya dan Bali\",\"text_position\":\"left\"}],\"bg_type\":\"image\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/map-indonesia-dots.svg\",\"bg_position\":\"center\"}', 2, 1, '2025-10-26 14:06:29', '2025-11-26 09:55:36'),
(212, 41, 'list_services', '{\"show_intro\":\"true\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"PRODUCT\",\"id\":\"PRODUK\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Discover Our Services at Linknet Media\",\"id\":\"Temukan Layanan Kami di Linknet Media\"},\"services\":[{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/values\\/values-customers.png\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"OTT Streaming Solutions\",\"id\":\"OTT Streaming Solutions\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"A solution that provides First Media TV channel services as well as Video on Demand (VoD) channels by utilizing existing Wi-Fi services at the customer\'s location.\",\"id\":\"A solution that provides First Media TV channel services as well as Video on Demand (VoD) channels by utilizing existing Wi-Fi services at the customer\'s location.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"One Stream\",\"id\":\"One Stream\"}}],\"other_count\":null},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"IPTV Content Services\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Revolutionizing family entertainment with an all-in-one platform in a compact box, offering diverse content for all ages.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"IPTV\",\"id\":\"IPTV\"}}],\"other_count\":null},{\"show_icon\":false,\"show_title\":true,\"show_description\":true,\"show_cta\":true,\"show_products\":true,\"show_others\":true,\"icon\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"Hospitality Entertainment\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Provides tailored entertainment solutions for hotels and accommodations, enhancing guest experiences through a wide range of channels, on-demand content, and interactive features.\"},\"button_text\":{\"en\":\"Explore Services\",\"id\":\"Jelajahi Layanan\"},\"button_url\":\"#\",\"products\":[{\"name\":{\"en\":\"Hospitality Entertainment\",\"id\":\"Hospitality Entertainment\"}}],\"other_count\":null}]}', 3, 1, '2025-10-26 14:21:32', '2026-01-14 07:41:19'),
(213, 41, 'info_contacts', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":\"lnSection__infoContact\",\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"true\",\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Get More Information about Linknet MediaCo\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Have questions or need more information? Our team is here to help. Reach out to us and we\'ll respond as soon as possible.\"},\"show_contacts_section\":\"true\",\"contact_items\":[{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/world.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Website\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"media.linknet.co.id\"},\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/media.linknet.co.id\",\"target\":\"_blank\"},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/phone.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Phone\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"(021) 2994 0808\"},\"url\":\"tel:+622129940808\",\"target\":null},{\"show_item\":true,\"show_icon\":false,\"icon\":\"src\\/assets\\/icons\\/mail.svg\",\"label\":{\"en\":\"Email\"},\"value\":{\"en\":\"media.inquiry@linknet.co.id\"},\"url\":\"mailto:media.inquiry@linknet.co.id\",\"target\":null}]}', 4, 1, '2025-10-26 14:55:12', '2026-01-19 01:42:59');
INSERT INTO `page_components` (`id`, `page_id`, `component_type`, `component_data`, `sort_order`, `is_visible`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(214, 14, 'information_list', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"false\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"MEDIA & ACTIVITIES\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Keep up with what\'s happening at Linknet\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Stay Update\"},\"info_sections\":[{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"Structure\",\"title_id\":\"Struktur\",\"content\":\"<figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img style=\\\"aspect-ratio:672\\/479;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/image%2016.png\\\" width=\\\"672\\\" height=\\\"479\\\"><\\/figure>\",\"content_id\":null,\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"RAPAT UMUM PEMEGANG SAHAM\",\"title_id\":null,\"content\":\"<p>The General Meeting of Shareholders (GMS) is the executor holding the highest power and authority in the Company. The authority of the General Meeting of Shareholders includes among others appointing and dismissing members of the Board of Commissioners and the Board of Directors, evaluate the performance of the Board of Commissioners and the Board of Directors, approve the amendments to the Articles of Association, approve the annual report and determine the form and amount of remuneration for the members of the Board of Commissioners and the Board of Directors.<\\/p><p>Learn more about GMS: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/investor\\/gms-announcement\\\"><strong>Click here for detailed information<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Rapat Umum Pemegang Saham (RUPS) adalah pelaksana yang memegang kekuasaan dan wewenang tertinggi dalam Perusahaan. Wewenang RUPS antara lain meliputi pengangkatan dan pemberhentian anggota Dewan Komisaris dan Direksi, mengevaluasi kinerja Dewan Komisaris dan Direksi, menyetujui perubahan Anggaran Dasar, menyetujui laporan tahunan, serta menetapkan bentuk dan jumlah remunerasi bagi anggota Dewan Komisaris dan Direksi.<\\/p><p>Cari tahu tentang RUPS: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/investor\\/gms-announcement\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat detail RUPS<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS\",\"title_id\":\"DEWAN KOMISARIS\",\"content\":\"<p>In accordance to the prevailing laws and regulations, the Board of Commissioners is the company\\u2019s organ comprising of representations of the Shareholders to carry out the supervisory function over the execution of the company\\u2019s policy and strategy by the Board of Directors and providing direction\\/advice to the Board of Directors in managing the Company based on the principles of good faith, prudency and accountability, and carry out the function to strengthen the Company\\u2019s image in the eyes of the public and the shareholders.<\\/p><p>The composition of Board of Commissioners: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Click here to see the composition of Board of Commissioners<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Sesuai dengan peraturan perundang-undangan yang berlaku, Dewan Komisaris merupakan organ perusahaan yang mewakili para Pemegang Saham untuk menjalankan fungsi pengawasan atas pelaksanaan kebijakan dan strategi perusahaan oleh Direksi, serta memberikan arahan atau nasihat kepada Direksi dalam mengelola Perusahaan berdasarkan prinsip itikad baik, kehati-hatian, dan akuntabilitas. Dewan Komisaris juga menjalankan fungsi untuk memperkuat citra Perusahaan di mata publik dan para pemegang saham.<\\/p><p>Susunan Dewan Komisaris: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat susunan Dewan Komisaris<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"AUDIT COMMITTEE\",\"title_id\":\"KOMITE AUDIT\",\"content\":\"<p>In accordance to regulations issued by the Financial Service Authority (Otoritas Jasa Keuangan) No.55\\/POJK.04, dated 23 December 2015 regarding Establishment and Implementation Guidelines for the Audit Committee Works, the establishment of the Audit Committee aims to ensure the implementation of corporate governance. The main duty of the Audit Committee is to encourage the implementation of good corporate governance, the establishment of proper internal control structure, the improvement of the quality of transparency and financial reports as well as review the public accountant\\u2019s scope, accuracy, independency and objectivity. The Audit Committee comprises of two members, who are independent parties having competence in accounting and finance, and is headed by the Independent Commissioner.<\\/p><p>The Board of Commissioners has established the Audit Committee as a support in performing its duties and obligations. The establishment of the Audit Committee is performed through a Decision Letter by the Board of Commissioners and is headed by one of the Independent Commissioners who are appointed by the Board of Commissioners.<\\/p><p>In exercising its authority, the Audit Committee is obliged to cooperate with other parties which are performing the Internal Audit function. The Audit Committee has 3 (three) members, comprising of 1 (one) Chairman, who is also serving as the Independent Commissioner, and 2 (two) members who are independent. All members of the Audit Committee have met independence, skills, experiences and integrity criteria as required by the regulations.<\\/p><p>The composition of Audit Committee: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Click here to see the composition of Audit Committee<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Sesuai dengan peraturan yang diterbitkan oleh <strong>Otoritas Jasa Keuangan (OJK)<\\/strong> No. 55\\/POJK.04 tanggal 23 Desember 2015 tentang <i>Pedoman Pembentukan dan Pedoman Pelaksanaan Kerja Komite Audit<\\/i>, pembentukan Komite Audit bertujuan untuk memastikan penerapan tata kelola perusahaan yang baik. Tugas utama Komite Audit adalah mendorong penerapan prinsip-prinsip <i>good corporate governance<\\/i>, pembentukan struktur pengendalian internal yang memadai, peningkatan kualitas transparansi dan laporan keuangan, serta menelaah ruang lingkup, ketepatan, independensi, dan objektivitas akuntan publik.<\\/p><p>Komite Audit terdiri dari dua anggota yang merupakan pihak independen dengan kompetensi di bidang akuntansi dan keuangan, serta diketuai oleh Komisaris Independen.<\\/p><p>Dewan Komisaris telah membentuk Komite Audit sebagai pendukung dalam melaksanakan tugas dan tanggung jawabnya. Pembentukan Komite Audit dilakukan melalui Surat Keputusan Dewan Komisaris dan dipimpin oleh salah satu Komisaris Independen yang ditunjuk oleh Dewan Komisaris.<\\/p><p>Dalam menjalankan kewenangannya, Komite Audit wajib bekerja sama dengan pihak lain yang menjalankan fungsi Audit Internal. Komite Audit memiliki <strong>3 (tiga)<\\/strong> anggota, yang terdiri dari <strong>1 (satu)<\\/strong> Ketua yang juga menjabat sebagai Komisaris Independen, serta <strong>2 (dua)<\\/strong> anggota yang merupakan pihak independen. Seluruh anggota Komite Audit telah memenuhi kriteria independensi, kemampuan, pengalaman, dan integritas sebagaimana dipersyaratkan oleh peraturan yang berlaku.<\\/p><p>Susunan Komite Audit: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat susunan Komite Audit<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"NOMINATION AND REMUNERATION COMMITTEE\",\"title_id\":\"KOMITE NOMINASI DAN REMUNERASI\",\"content\":\"<p>Nomination and Remuneration Committee is a committee established by and responsible to the Board of Commissioners, based on Indonesian Financial Services Authority Regulation No. 34\\/POJK.04\\/2014 on Nominating and Remuneration Committee of Public Company dated on December 2014. The establishment of the Nomination and Remuneration Committee is an integral part of the Company\\u2019s efforts to implement the principles of good corporate governance (GCG), which covers aspects of transparency, accountability, responsibility, independence and fairness, justice and equity.<\\/p><p>The composition of Nomination and Remuneration: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Click here to see the composition Nomination and Remuneration<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Komite Nominasi dan Remunerasi adalah komite yang dibentuk oleh dan bertanggung jawab kepada Dewan Komisaris, berdasarkan Peraturan Otoritas Jasa Keuangan Republik Indonesia No. 34\\/POJK.04\\/2014 tentang Komite Nominasi dan Remunerasi Emiten atau Perusahaan Publik yang diterbitkan pada Desember 2014. Pembentukan Komite Nominasi dan Remunerasi merupakan bagian yang tidak terpisahkan dari upaya Perusahaan dalam menerapkan prinsip-prinsip good corporate governance (GCG), yang mencakup aspek transparansi, akuntabilitas, tanggung jawab, independensi, serta kewajaran dan kesetaraan.<\\/p><p>Susunan Komite Nominasi dan Remunerasi: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat susunan Komite Nominasi dan Remunerasi.<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"BOARD OF DIRECTORS\",\"title_id\":\"DEWAN DIREKTUR\",\"content\":\"<p>The Board of Directors is a company organ that holds full responsibility over the management of the company in keeping at all times with the interests and goal of the Company and its business units as well as taking into consideration the interests of all shareholders and stakeholders. The Board of Directors\\u2019 responsibility shall include conducting internal supervision effectively and efficiently; monitoring risks and managing them, maintaining a conducive working environment to improve productivity and professionalism, managing staffs and reporting the Company\\u2019s entire performance to the shareholders in the General Meeting of Shareholders.<\\/p><p>The composition of Board of Director: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Click here to see the composition Board of Director<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Direksi adalah organ perusahaan yang memegang tanggung jawab penuh atas pengelolaan perusahaan dengan senantiasa menjaga kepentingan dan tujuan Perusahaan beserta unit-unit bisnisnya, serta mempertimbangkan kepentingan seluruh pemegang saham dan pemangku kepentingan. Tanggung jawab Direksi mencakup pelaksanaan pengawasan internal secara efektif dan efisien; memantau serta mengelola risiko; menjaga lingkungan kerja yang kondusif untuk meningkatkan produktivitas dan profesionalisme; mengelola karyawan; serta melaporkan seluruh kinerja Perusahaan kepada para pemegang saham dalam Rapat Umum Pemegang Saham (RUPS).<\\/p><p>Susunan Direksi: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat susunan Direksi<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"CORPORATE SECRETARY\",\"title_id\":\"SEKRETARIS PERUSAHAAN\",\"content\":\"<p>With reference to the Indonesian Financial Services Authority (Otoritas Jasa Keuangan\\/OJK) Regulation No. 35\\/POJK.04\\/2014 and the Regulation of PT Bursa Efek Indonesia (Indonesia Stock Exchange\\/BEI) No. I-A, the Company shall appoint a Corporate Secretary who shall serve as the liaison officer between the Company and the Company\\u2019s Executor and stakeholders. Public and\\/or investors may access the Company\\u2019s web site to obtain information on the Company\\u2019s business activities, or contact the Corporate Secretary to obtain more information on the Company.<\\/p><p>Profile of Corporate Secretary:&nbsp; <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Click here to see Profile of Corporate Secretary<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Mengacu pada Peraturan Otoritas Jasa Keuangan (OJK) No. 35\\/POJK.04\\/2014 dan Peraturan PT Bursa Efek Indonesia (BEI) No. I-A, Perusahaan wajib menunjuk seorang Sekretaris Perusahaan (Corporate Secretary) yang berfungsi sebagai penghubung antara Perusahaan dengan Organ Perusahaan serta para pemangku kepentingan. Publik dan\\/atau investor dapat mengakses situs web Perusahaan untuk memperoleh informasi mengenai kegiatan usaha Perusahaan, atau menghubungi Sekretaris Perusahaan untuk mendapatkan informasi lebih lanjut mengenai Perusahaan.<\\/p><p>Profil Sekretaris Perusahaan: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/about\\/management\\\"><strong>Klik di sini untuk melihat Profil Sekretaris Perusahaan.<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"INTERNAL AUDIT\",\"title_id\":\"AUDIT INTERNAL\",\"content\":\"<p>The establishment and guidelines for the preparation of the Charter of the Internal Audit Unit refers to regulation of Financial Services Authority Regulation No. 56\\/POJK.04\\/2015 dated 29 December 2015 regarding the establishment and guidelines on the arrangement of the certificates for the internal audit unit. The internal Audit Unit has tasks, among others, to test and evaluate the implementation of internal control and risks management system in accordance with the company\\u2019s policies as well as performing examination and judgment over the efficiency and effectiveness in finance, accounting, operational, human resources, marketing, information technology and other activities. In performing the duties, the Internal Audit Unit will always in cooperation with the Audit Committee and is responsible to the President Director. The establishment of the Internal Audit Unit is a realization of the company\\u2019s commitment to create the good and efficient corporate governance.<\\/p><p>Audit Internal Charter: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/\\/files\\/document\\/governance\\/LN%20Internal%20Audit%20Charter%20vF.pdf?_t=1711435776\\\"><strong>Click here to see Audit Internal Charter<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Pembentukan dan pedoman penyusunan Piagam Unit Audit Internal mengacu pada Peraturan Otoritas Jasa Keuangan No. 56\\/POJK.04\\/2015 tanggal 29 Desember 2015 mengenai pembentukan dan pedoman penyusunan piagam unit audit internal. Unit Audit Internal memiliki tugas antara lain menguji dan mengevaluasi pelaksanaan pengendalian internal dan sistem manajemen risiko sesuai dengan kebijakan perusahaan, serta melakukan pemeriksaan dan penilaian atas efisiensi dan efektivitas di bidang keuangan, akuntansi, operasional, sumber daya manusia, pemasaran, teknologi informasi, dan aktivitas lainnya.<\\/p><p>Dalam melaksanakan tugasnya, Unit Audit Internal senantiasa bekerja sama dengan Komite Audit dan bertanggung jawab kepada Direktur Utama. Pembentukan Unit Audit Internal merupakan wujud komitmen perusahaan untuk mewujudkan tata kelola perusahaan yang baik dan efisien.<\\/p><p>Piagam Audit Internal: <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/\\/files\\/document\\/governance\\/LN%20Internal%20Audit%20Charter%20vF.pdf?_t=1711435776\\\"><strong>Klik di sii untuk melihat Piagam Audit Internal<\\/strong><\\/a><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"INDEPENDENT AUDITOR\",\"title_id\":\"AUDITOR INDEPENDEN\",\"content\":\"<p>With reference to the Financial Services Authority Regulation No. 9 TAHUN 2023 concerning the Use of Public Accountant Services and Public Accounting Firm in Financial Services Activities dated 11 July 2023. The General Meeting of Shareholders must decide on the appointment of AP and\\/or KAP that will provide audit services for annual historical financial information by considering the proposals of the board of commissioners, supervisory board, or parties that perform supervisory functions as carried out by the board of commissioners.<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Mengacu pada Peraturan Otoritas Jasa Keuangan No. 9 Tahun 2023 tentang Penggunaan Jasa Akuntan Publik dan Kantor Akuntan Publik dalam Kegiatan Jasa Keuangan tanggal 11 Juli 2023, Rapat Umum Pemegang Saham (RUPS) harus menetapkan penunjukan Akuntan Publik (AP) dan\\/atau Kantor Akuntan Publik (KAP) yang akan memberikan jasa audit atas informasi keuangan historis tahunan dengan mempertimbangkan usulan dari Dewan Komisaris, Dewan Pengawas, atau pihak-pihak yang menjalankan fungsi pengawasan sebagaimana dilakukan oleh Dewan Komisaris.<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"}]}', 2, 1, '2025-11-25 16:19:48', '2025-12-04 00:54:21'),
(215, 42, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"background_image_mobile\":null,\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"false\",\"title\":{\"en\":\"Summary of Standardization\",\"id\":\"Ringkasan Standardisasi\"},\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_link\":null,\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-11-25 16:25:01', '2025-12-19 10:57:50'),
(216, 42, 'information_list', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"false\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"MEDIA & ACTIVITIES\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Keep up with what\'s happening at Linknet\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Stay Update\"},\"info_sections\":[{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"ISO 9001:2015 Quality Management Systems\",\"title_id\":\"ISO 9001:2015 Sistem Manajemen Mutu\",\"content\":\"<p>The Company has been certified with ISO 9001:2015 since 2004 by United Registrar of Systems Ltd. (URS), in recognition of its implementation of a Quality Management System (QMS) in the provision of internet data and cable TV services.<\\/p><p>In 2022, the Company migrated its certification body from United Registrar of Systems Ltd. (URS) to PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia. Subsequently, in 2025, the Company was recertified by PT BSI Group Indonesia in recognition of its implementation of QMS in The provision of wired telecommunications activities, internet service provider (internet access services), Connection &amp; ICT Solution (Communication System services), internet interconnection services (NAP) and other multimedia services.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/iso1.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"509\\\"><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perseroan telah memperoleh sertifikasi ISO 9001:2015 sejak tahun 2004 dari United Registrar of Systems Ltd. (URS) sebagai pengakuan atas penerapan Sistem Manajemen Mutu (SMM) dalam penyediaan layanan data internet dan TV kabel.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Pada tahun 2022, Perseroan melakukan migrasi badan sertifikasi dari United Registrar of Systems Ltd. (URS) ke PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia. Selanjutnya, pada tahun 2025, Perseroan kembali memperoleh sertifikasi dari PT BSI Group Indonesia sebagai pengakuan atas penerapan SMM dalam kegiatan penyediaan aktivitas telekomunikasi kabel, penyedia layanan internet (layanan akses internet), koneksi dan solusi ICT (layanan sistem komunikasi), layanan interkoneksi internet (NAP) dan layanan multimedia lainnya.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/iso1.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"509\\\"><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"false\",\"title\":\"ISO 37001:2016 Anti-Bribery Management Systems\",\"title_id\":\"ISO 37001:2016 Sistem Manajemen Anti Penyuapan\",\"content\":\"<p>The Company has obtained International Standard Operation certification for ISO \\/ IEC 37001:2016 in 2023 from PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia as recognition of Anti Bribery Management System regarding the provision of internet provider and cable TV sevices with activities including Procurement, Business Process Improvement, Finance &amp; Accounting and Internal Audit function at Head Office.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/image%2018.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"506\\\"><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perseroan telah memperoleh sertifikasi International Standard Operation untuk ISO 37001:2016 pada tahun 2023 dari PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia sebagai pengakuan Sistem Manajemen Anti Penyuapan terkait penyediaan penyedia internet dan layanan TV kabel dengan kegiatan meliputi Procurement, Business Process Improvement, Finance &amp; Accounting, dan Internal Audit di Kantor Pusat.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/image%2018.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"506\\\"><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"ISO 14001:2015 Environmental Management Systems\",\"title_id\":\"ISO 14001:2015 Sistem Manajemen Lingkungan\",\"content\":\"<p>The company has obtained International Standard Operation certification for ISO 14001:2015 in 2019 from PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia as recognition of Environmental Management Systems (EMS).&nbsp;<\\/p><p>In 2025, the company has extend the scope of EMS from the provision of internet data provider and TV cable services to The provision of wired telecommunications activities, internet service provider (internet access services), communication system services, internet interconnection services (NAP), other multimedia services, and satellite telecommunications activities.<\\/p><p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/iso-14001.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"511\\\"><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perusahaan telah memperoleh sertifikasi Standar Operasional Internasional ISO 14001:2015 pada tahun 2019 dari PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia sebagai pengakuan atas penerapan Sistem Manajemen Lingkungan (Environmental Management Systems\\/EMS).&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Pada tahun 2025, perusahaan telah memperluas cakupan EMS dari layanan penyedia data internet dan TV kabel menjadi Penyediaan kegiatan telekomunikasi kabel, penyedia layanan internet (layanan akses internet), layanan sistem komunikasi, layanan interkoneksi internet (NAP), layanan multimedia lainnya, dan kegiatan telekomunikasi satelit.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/iso-14001.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"511\\\"><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"ISO 45001:2018 Occupational Health and Safety Management Systems\",\"title_id\":\"ISO 45001:2018 Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja\",\"content\":\"<p>The company has obtained International Standard Operation certification for ISO \\/ IEC 45000:2018 in 2022 from PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia as recognition of Occupational Safety &amp; Health Management System regarding the provision of Head Office for internet data provider and TV cable services.<\\/p><p>In 2025, the company has extend the scope of OHS from the provision of internet data provider and TV cable services to The provision of wired telecommunications activities, internet service provider (internet access services), communication system services, internet interconnection services (NAP), other multimedia services, and satellite telecommunications activities for head office activities.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/iso-45001.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"509\\\"><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perusahaan telah memperoleh sertifikasi Standar Operasional Internasional ISO\\/IEC 45000:2018 pada tahun 2022 dari PT British Standards Institution (BSI) Group Indonesia sebagai pengakuan atas Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja (K3) terkait penyediaan Kantor Pusat untuk layanan penyedia data internet dan TV kabel.<\\/p><p>Pada tahun 2025, perusahaan telah memperluas cakupan K3 dari penyediaan layanan data internet dan TV kabel menjadi penyediaan kegiatan telekomunikasi kabel, penyedia layanan internet (layanan akses internet), layanan sistem komunikasi, layanan interkoneksi internet (NAP), layanan multimedia lainnya, dan kegiatan telekomunikasi satelit untuk aktivitas Kantor Pusat.<br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/iso-45001.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"509\\\"><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"SMK3 Occupational Health and Safety Management Systems which refer to (Government Regulation (Indonesia) No. 50 Year 2012\",\"title_id\":\"SMK3 Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja merujuk kepada PP 50 Tahun 2012.\",\"content\":\"<p>The company has obtained Government Standard certification for Occupational Safety &amp; Health Management System from Indonesian Minister of Employment of the Republic of Indonesia as recognition related to implementation of Occupational Safety &amp; Health for Link Net in accordance with PP No. 50 Year 2012.<br><br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/smk-3.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"550\\\"><\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>Perseroan telah memperoleh sertifikasi Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja Karyawan pada tahun 2019 dari Kementerian Ketenagakerjaan RI untuk penerapan K3 Karyawan Link Net berbasis PP Nomor 50 Tahun 2012.<br><br><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/sertifikat\\/smk-3.png\\\" width=\\\"360\\\" height=\\\"550\\\"><\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"}]}', 2, 1, '2025-11-25 16:25:10', '2025-12-19 07:34:57'),
(217, 43, 'hero_section', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"aria_label\":\"Our Vision\",\"background_image\":\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/1\\/herosliders\\/corpins.png\",\"bg_position_desktop\":\"center\",\"bg_position_mobile\":\"center\",\"size_hero\":\"lnHero__small\",\"theme\":\"dark\",\"gradient_visible\":\"true\",\"minilogo_visible\":\"false\",\"minilogo_image\":null,\"pill_visible\":\"false\",\"subtitle\":null,\"subtitle_id\":null,\"title\":\"Linknet Policy\",\"title_id\":\"Kebijakan Linknet\",\"description\":null,\"description_id\":null,\"description_width\":\"w-75\",\"button_visible\":\"false\",\"button_text\":\"Get to Know Us\",\"button_text_id\":null,\"button_link\":\"#\",\"button_icon\":\"arrow-top-right.svg\",\"button_size\":\"btn-lg\"}', 1, 1, '2025-11-25 16:30:26', '2025-11-26 08:15:52'),
(218, 43, 'information_list', '{\"custom_id\":null,\"custom_class\":null,\"bg_type\":\"color\",\"bg_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_color_text\":\"#ffffff\",\"bg_image\":null,\"bg_position\":\"center\",\"show_intro_section\":\"false\",\"intro_label\":{\"en\":\"MEDIA & ACTIVITIES\"},\"intro_title\":{\"en\":\"Keep up with what\'s happening at Linknet\"},\"intro_description\":{\"en\":\"Stay Update\"},\"info_sections\":[{\"show_section\":\"false\",\"title\":\"POLICY FOR STANDARDIZATION OF MANAGEMENT SYSTEM\",\"title_id\":\"KEBIJAKAN STANDARISASI SISTEM MANAJEMEN\",\"content\":\"<p>PT Link Net Tbk (\\u201cLinknet\\u201d) is running business in the high-speed broadband internet service provider business in Indonesia, and also enters into cooperation with PT First Media Television as paid television service provider.<\\/p><p>Linknet is committed to apply the standard-based Integrated Management System standard ISO 37001:2016 for the provision of data provider and tv cable internet service for Business Process Improvement function in office center, ISO 9001:2015 for provision of internet data provider and cable TV services, ISO standard 20000-1:2018 for IT &amp; Services Service Management System in providing Subscribers Management System Service in Linknet, ISO standard 27001:2013 for Operational Data Center to support the Subscribers Management System Service, and ISO standard 14001:2015 for the provision of internet data and cable TV services, ISO standard 45001:2018 for the provision of data internet and cable TV services at the head office and PP Number 50 of 2012 for Occupational Health and Safety Management System Standard (SMK3).<\\/p>\",\"content_id\":\"<p>PT Link Net Tbk (\\u201cLinknet\\u201d) bergerak di bidang usaha penyedia layanan internet <i>broadband<\\/i> berkecepatan tinggi di Indonesia, dan juga bekerja sama dengan PT First Media Television sebagai penyedia layanan televisi berbayar.<\\/p><p>Linknet berkomitmen untuk menerapkan <i>Integrated Management System<\\/i> berbasis standar standar ISO 37001:2016 untuk penyediaan layanan internet data provider dan <i>Cable TV<\\/i> untuk fungsi <i>Business Process Improvement<\\/i> di kantor pusat, ISO 9001:2015 untuk penyediaan internet data provider dan layanan <i>cable TV<\\/i>, standar ISO 20000-1:2018 untuk Sistem Manajemen Layanan IT &amp; Services dalam menyediakan Layanan Subscribers Management System di Linknet, standar ISO 27001:2013 untuk Operasional Data Center untuk mendukung Layanan Subscibers Management System, dan standar ISO 14001:2015 untuk penyediaan internet data provider dan layanan cable TV, standar ISO 45001:2018 untuk penyediaan internet data dan layanan Cable TV di kantor pusat dan PP Nomor 50 Tahun 2012 untuk Standar Sistem Manajemen Keselamatan dan Kesehatan Kerja (SMK3).<\\/p>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"},{\"show_section\":\"true\",\"title\":\"The application of Integrated Management System encourages Linknet to fulfill the commitments of:\",\"title_id\":\"Penerapan Integrated Management System mendorong LinkNet untuk memenuhi komitmen:\",\"content\":\"<ol><li>Providing corporate governance that supports the achievement of the company\\u2019s anti-bribery objectives and the implementation of Good Corporate Governance principles;<\\/li><li>Implementing and developing the Integrated Management System (IMS) in accordance with applicable regulations and standards;<\\/li><li>Upholding a commitment to comply with the code of ethics, professional responsibilities, and the effective development of competencies;<\\/li><li>Prohibiting any form of bribery and similar practices within the company;<\\/li><li>Aligning anti-bribery policies with the company\\u2019s objectives;<\\/li><li>Ensuring commitment to fulfilling the requirements of the Anti-Bribery Management System;<\\/li><li>Promoting increased anti-bribery awareness among relevant stakeholders;<\\/li><li>Implementing the principles of continuous improvement within the Anti-Bribery Management System;<\\/li><li>Granting responsibility, authority, and independence to the Anti-Bribery Compliance Function (FKAP);<\\/li><li>Imposing strict sanctions on violations of the Anti-Bribery Management System policy;<\\/li><li>Realizing the planning, implementation, and evaluation of goods and services procurement processes by applying sustainable process principles;<\\/li><li>Providing the best, high-quality, highly consistent, and environmentally friendly services;<\\/li><li>Delivering information technology services within an internationally standardized service catalogue aligned with user expectations;<\\/li><li>Ensuring information security to safeguard data and information;<\\/li><li>Providing an environmentally friendly workplace to support environmental preservation and prevent environmental damage or pollution in accordance with the organization\\u2019s context;<\\/li><li>Providing a safe, healthy, respectful, and responsible work environment to prevent workplace accidents and occupational diseases, and to foster a synergistic workplace culture;<\\/li><li>Applying risk controls through target measurements and corporate programs to achieve integrity, sustainable goods and services procurement, customer satisfaction, quality technology services, information security, and to minimize hazards and reduce occupational health and safety risks as well as environmental security risks;<\\/li><li>Complying with applicable laws and regulations related to anti-bribery, procurement of goods and services, quality, service performance, technology, information security, environmental sustainability, and occupational health and safety;<\\/li><li>Communicating company regulations, provisions, and policies, and facilitating communication and participation from relevant parties;<\\/li><li><p>Regularly monitoring performance and driving continuous improvement to ensure ongoing relevance and suitability for the organization.<\\/p><p>This Integrated Management System policy applies to all employees and stakeholders within Linknet. It is documented, communicated, maintained, and periodically reviewed in accordance with changes in legislation, technology, processes, or other relevant factors to ensure continual enhancement.<\\/p><p><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/gms\\/eng\\/202505_AGMS%2021%20May\\/20250414LINK%20Pengumuman%20RUPST.pdf\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/pdf.svg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"44\\\" height=\\\"44\\\"><\\/a><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/policy\\/Anti-Bribery-and-Anti-Corruption-Policy-V3.pdf\\\">ANTI-BRIBERY AND ANTI-CORRUPTION POLICY<\\/a><\\/p><p><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/gms\\/eng\\/202505_AGMS%2021%20May\\/20250414LINK%20Pengumuman%20RUPST.pdf\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/pdf.svg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"44\\\" height=\\\"44\\\"><\\/a><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/policy\\/Gifts-Donations-and-Sponsorships-Policy-V2.pdf\\\">GIFTS, DONATIONS &amp; SPONSORSHIPS POLICY<\\/a><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"content_id\":\"<ol><li>Menyediakan tata kelola perusahaan yang mendukung tercapainya tujuan anti penyuapan perusahaan serta penerapan prinsip-prinsip Good Corporate Governance;<\\/li><li>Menerapkan dan mengembangkan <i>Integrated Management System (IMS)<\\/i> sesuai ketentuan dan standar yang berlaku;<\\/li><li>Menerapkan komitmen untuk memenuhi kode etik, tanggung jawab profesional dan pengembangan kompetensi yang efektif;<\\/li><li>Melarang praktek-praktek penyuapan dan sejenis di lingkungan perusahaan<\\/li><li>Menselaraskan kebijakan anti penyuapan dengan tujuan perusahaan;<\\/li><li>Memastikan komitmen kepada pemenuhan persyaratan Sistem Manajemen Anti Penyuapan;<\\/li><li>Mendorong peningkatan kesadaran anti penyuapan kepada jajaran stakeholder terkait;<\\/li><li>Menjalankan prinsip perbaikan berkelanjutan dalam Sistem Manajemen Anti Penyuapan;<\\/li><li>Memberikan tanggung jawab, kewenangan dan independensi kepada Fungsi kepatuhan Anti Penyuapan (FKAP);<\\/li><li>Memberikan sanksi tegas kepada pelanggar ketentuan dalam kebijakan Sistem Manajemen Anti Penyuapan;<\\/li><li>Mewujudkan perencanaan, pelaksanaan dan evaluasi proses pengadaaan barang dan jasa dengan memperhatikan prinsip \\u2013 prinsip proses berkesinambungan;<\\/li><li>Menyediakan pelayanan terbaik, bermutu tinggi dan konsistensi tinggi serta ramah lingkungan;<\\/li><li>Menyelenggarakan layanan teknologi informasi dalam service catalogue berstandar internasional sesuai dengan harapan pengguna layanan;<\\/li><li>Menjamin keamanan informasi untuk pengamanan data dan informasi;<\\/li><li>Menyediakan lingkungan kerja yang ramah lingkungan untuk melestarikan lingkungan hidup dan mencegah terjadinya kerusakan atau pencemaran lingkungan sesuai konteks organisasi;<\\/li><li>Menyediakan lingkungan kerja yang aman, sehat, saling menghargai\\/menghormati, dan bertanggung jawab untuk mencegah kecelakaan dan penyakit akibat kerja (PAK) serta mewujudkan lingkungan kerja yang sinergis;<\\/li><li>Menerapkan pengendalian risiko melalui pengukuran sasaran dan program perusahaan untuk mewujudkan integritas, pengadaan barang dan jasa yang berkelanjutan, memberikan kepuasan Pelanggan, menyediakan kualitas layanan teknologi, memastikan keamanan informasi serta meminimalkan bahaya dan mengurangi risiko keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja serta keamanan lingkungan;<\\/li><li>Mematuhi peraturan perundangan dan persyaratan yang berlaku terkait anti penyuapan, pengadaan terkait barang dan jasa, mutu, kualitas layanan, teknologi, keamanan informasi, kelestarian lingkungan hidup dan keselamatan dan kesehatan kerja;<\\/li><li>Menginformasikan peraturan, ketentuan dan kebijakan yang berlaku dalam perusahaan serta mengakomodir komunikasi serta partisipasi dari pihak \\u2013 pihak terkait;<\\/li><li><p>Secara regular melakukan pemantauan kinerja dan perbaikan berkelanjutan agar tetap relevan dan sesuai untuk organisasi.<\\/p><p>Kebijakan penerapan <i>Integrated Management System<\\/i> ini berlaku untuk karyawan dan para pemangku kepentingan di lingkungan Linknet. Kebijakan ini didokumentasikan, dikomunikasikan, dipelihara dan ditinjau secara berkala sesuai dengan perubahan yang terjadi dalam peraturan perundangan, teknologi, proses atau lainnya untuk disempurnakan.<\\/p><p><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/gms\\/eng\\/202505_AGMS%2021%20May\\/20250414LINK%20Pengumuman%20RUPST.pdf\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/pdf.svg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"44\\\" height=\\\"44\\\"><\\/a><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/policy\\/Anti-Bribery-and-Anti-Corruption-Policy-V3.pdf\\\">KEBIJAKAN ANTI SUAP DAN ANTI KORUPSI<\\/a><\\/p><p><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/gms\\/eng\\/202505_AGMS%2021%20May\\/20250414LINK%20Pengumuman%20RUPST.pdf\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/frontend\\/src\\/assets\\/img\\/pdf.svg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"44\\\" height=\\\"44\\\"><\\/a><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/linknet.co.id\\/storage\\/files\\/document\\/announcement\\/policy\\/Gifts-Donations-and-Sponsorships-Policy-V2.pdf\\\">KEBIJAKAN HADIAH, DONASI DAN SPONSOR<\\/a><\\/p><\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"show_cta\":\"false\",\"cta_text\":\"Learn More\",\"cta_link\":null,\"cta_icon\":\"arrow-right.svg\",\"show_related_articles\":\"false\",\"show_documents\":\"false\"}]}', 2, 1, '2025-11-25 16:31:18', '2025-12-19 08:06:28'),
